	(2000000381, 'An external influence under illusory guise of Thorim\'s deceased mate Sif has been detected.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000382, 'Mental interference from this presence dangerously close from triggering partial memory damage.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000383, 'Tactical analysis suggest approaching the arena from the front and splitting secondary force through a side passage at the ground level. This will maximize odds of reaching Thorim\'s outlook before mental domination by external presence is complete.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000403, 'New orders! Unlock the entry to the Celestial Planetarium.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000408, 'Request denied. Access requires manual verification of the four watchers\' sigils.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000404, 'Four watchers? Sigils? Could ye be a little less cryptic, confounded machine?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000409, 'The four watchers of Ulduar: Freya, Thorim, Hodir and Mimiron. The sigils are tied to their physical and mental integrity. All four sigils are required for access to the Celestial Planetarium.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000405, 'How do we get the sigils from them, then? Just walk up to them and ask them nicely?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000410, 'Analyzing watchers status. Please wait.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000411, 'Corruption found. External influence gaining control over watchers. Sigils compromised.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000406, 'You\'re going to tell us how to... "un-compromise" the sigils, aren\'t you?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000412, 'Sufficient use of force would trigger a reset in watcher functions, removing the external influence.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000413, 'As for not endangering the sigils during this process, I can analyze each watcher\'s status and make that information available to you upon completion of calculations.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000407, 'I\'ve dreamed of roaming the halls of the titans for years. I never thought I\'d be pitted against their creations.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000414, 'What a fight you missed, Dorian! It was one for the ages!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Какой бой ты пропустил, Дориан! Такой раз в сто лет бывает!'),
	(2000000415, 'There we were, riding into battle at full speed on the back of Stampy...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Мы ворвались в бой на полном скаку, восседая на спине Топотуна:'),
	(2000000416, 'Everything was shaking all over the place. I could hardly steady my gun.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Все вокруг затряслось. Я с трудом удерживал свое ружье.'),
	(2000000417, 'And then we saw her, the fearsome beast!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'И тогда мы увидели ее, эту ужасную зверюгу!'),
	(2000000418, 'It took all of $N\'s skill to maintain control of Stampy.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '$N чудом удалось усмирить под собой Топотуна.'),
	(2000000419, 'The battle was a haze of blood, lead, and sweat. The broodmother\'s attacks came faster and faster!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Все смешалось: кровь, свинец, пот воинов. Праматерь атаковала все агрессивнее и агрессивнее!'),
	(2000000420, 'But, in the end, $N and I prevailed through our wits and teamwork. And now we have this glorious trophy as a memento of our victory.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Но в конце концов, мы с $N победили благодаря нашей смекалке и слаженности. На память об этой славной победе у нас остался этот великолепный трофей.'),
	(2000000421, 'Do I detect a bit of jealousy, Dorian?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Мне кажется, или ты немного завидуешь, Дориан?'),
	(2000000422, 'Well, I don\'t know. I was here tending the fire and discussing the drawbacks of cogs with Zootfizzle. That\'s pretty epic, too, in its own way.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ну, я не знаю. Вообще-то я следил за огнем и обсуждал с Любопытсоном все то зло, что таят в себе шестеренки. Это тоже по-своему эпично.'),
	(2000000423, 'Do not do anything that would the incite Horde. $N. The Warchief has agreed to see us on good faith.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Постарайтесь ничем не задеть орду. $N. Вождь проявил великодушие, согласившись на эту встречу.'),
	(2000000424, '%s begins a rite of creation...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000425, 'I have created the totem. You, $N, must cleanse the well.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000426, '%s creates a new totem...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000427, 'The totem is made, $N.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000428, '%s transforms the items $N gave him into a totem of cleansing...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000429, 'The totem is made. The well may now be cleansed.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000430, '%s stares to the northwest and lets out a long, drawn out howl.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000431, '%s lets forth a mighty howl.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000432, 'You\'re late, courier. No, I don\'t want any excuses; this errand is far too important.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ты опоздал, посланник. Нет, мне не нужны твои извинения. Это слишком важное задание.'),
	(2000000433, 'Here\'s the tome our representative brought from Wyrmrest. Get this to Myralion Sunblaze immediately.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Наш представитель привез эту книгу из Храма Драконьего Покоя. Немедленно доставь ее Миралию Блеску Солнца.'),
	(2000000434, 'Watch your back, courier. I needn\'t remind you of the value of the book, nor the fact that the Silver Covenant will stop at nothing to take it from us.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Будь осторожен, посланник. Не стоит лишний раз напоминать тебе о ценности книги, равно как и о том, что Серебряный союз не остановится ни перед чем, чтобы заполучить ее.'),
	(2000000435, 'Here is the book. You must ensure it gets to Caladis Brightspear in Icecrown before the Sunreavers realize what is happening.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Вот эта книга. Ты должен во что бы то ни стало доставить ее Каладису Сияющему Копью в Ледяную Корону, пока Похитители Солнца не узнали, что книга у нас.'),
	(2000000436, 'Travel quickly! The Sunreavers will not waste any time once they realize that we have the information they seek.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000437, 'Thank you, $N. Now, to perform the test...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000438, 'Ah, I see...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000439, 'Yes, this is unfortunate.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000440, '$N, I have confirmed that this blood is from the Bonechewer clan of orcs, tainted with demonic power. I\'m afraid, however, that my current equipment can delve no deeper into this mystery...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000441, 'Thank you, $N. It looks like they\'re going to get along just fine.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000442, 'I have an idea. Let\'s plant this shard in the ground and see what happens.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000443, 'The evil emanating from the crystal shard has lured one of the colossi. Put it down quick!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000444, 'There, it is completed.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000445, '$r, do you know who Kolphis Darkscale is?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000446, 'Yes, he\'s second-in-command of the wyrmcult at the Blackwing Coven to the west.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000447, 'The arakkoa are hidden... everywhere!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000448, 'Rest now, Adaris. You need to recover your strength.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005245, 'We\'d do well not to be reckless. There\'s still much to learn about this land and about the enemy.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005246, 'Prudence should not mean granting our enemy unnecessary advantages.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005247, 'We will act when we know what we need, old friend. The druids have proven wise and capable of making their own decisions.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005248, 'All my bags are packed, I\'m ready to go.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005249, 'The ship\'s not ready yet. We still need to calibrate the fuse length to make sure that it doesn\'t burn out and leave you up there alone.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005250, 'You need to do what? All this science. I don\'t understand... Look, this is just my job, five days a week.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005251, 'Essentially, it\'s going to be a long, long time till we are ready to launch. Maybe you should just head back home to your family.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005252, 'I can\'t. I\'m not the man they think I am at home. Besides, I didn\'t bring them out here.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
