	(2000005256, 'Oh no, no, no... I\'m a rocket man.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005257, 'Well, it\'s like I said; it\'s going to be a while before we get this ship ready for flight. We\'ll keep you informed.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005271, 'With all due respect, A\'dal sent us here to investigate Kael\'s activities, not mount a full-scaled attack.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005272, 'Look, sweetheart. No one\'s talking about storming Tempest Keep ourselves, but when we see a target of opportunity we have to take it.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005273, 'Hold your tongue, knave! Do not dare use that tone with a priestess of the Light!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005274, 'I\'m surrounded by idiots.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005275, 'The magistrix will be happy to know I\'m fluent in Thalassian. Your courtesy is not lost on me.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005276, 'Back to the topic... we should focus our attention on these manaforges. We need to learn what the enemy is doing with them and why.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005277, 'We\'ve told you all there is to know! Do you forget that many of us used to be trusted followers of Kael\'thas?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005278, '...and just look at where that got us!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005279, 'Even you must admit that your information from defectors is outdated and unreliable. Let us make calculated attacks on these manaforges and gather what information we can.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000005280, 'Finally some talk of action from the big guy!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000490, 'If you think I\'ll betray my friend that easily, think again! Face me, you scoundrel!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Думаешь, я так легко предам друга? Не дождешься! Защищайся, мелкая гнусь!'),
	(2000000449, 'I yield to you.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000450, 'Prepare yourself!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000451, 'Let it begin!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000453, 'Thanks, I should\'ve never left Silverpine Forest.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000454, 'You have my thanks!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000455, 'Thank you. I thought I was going to die.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000452, 'Rise, Sindragosa! Rise and lead the Frostbrood into war!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Восстань, Синдрагоса! Восстань и веди ледяных драконов в бой!'),
	(2000000456, 'Thank you all for coming tonight. Now put your hands together to welcome Shattrath\'s best, Perry Gatner!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000457, 'Perry Gatner! What an act! The cantina is open all night long, so please, stay and enjoy yourselves!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000458, 'Check out the comedy stylings of Perry Gatner in just a few minutes!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000459, 'If you are ready to laugh, head over to the World\'s End Tavern!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000460, 'Now, in Shattrath City: The Tauren Chieftains! Playing in the World\'s End Tavern at the top of the hour!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000461, 'Who? The Tauren Chieftains! What? A live performance. Where? The World\'s End Tavern! When? The top of the hour! BE THERE!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000462, 'Frenzyheart kill you if you come back. You no welcome here no more!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000464, 'Thanks, $R! I\'m sure my dad will reward you greatly! Bye!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000465, 'This is the last time I get caught! I promise! Bye!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000466, '%s smells the meat, awakens from his slumber, and roars in anger!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000074, 'Bat gizzards again for the gnomes tonight...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000467, 'What do they expect, making the bats come in at that angle? Broken necks and gamey bat stew, that\'s what they get.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000468, '\'We like trees, Fenrick. They provide cover.\' They won\'t let me chop them down, either.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000469, 'I wonder how many reinforcements need to suffer injury before they allows us to chop down these idiotic trees. They\'re costing us a fortune in bats. Maybe I\'ll rig a harness or two...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000470, 'ROARRRRR!!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000471, 'DARKSHIRE...I HUNGER!!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000472, 'Beware, $n! Look to the west!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000473, 'Watch your back. These Drakkari are a nasty lot.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000474, 'See you around.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000475, 'Right. I\'d better get back to the sergeant then.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000476, 'Are you $N? I heard you were dead.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000477, 'Thank you, $r. I will take this miserable cur from you now.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000478, 'Raliq teach you lesson now!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000479, 'F\'woooroonn! Coosh\'coosh pay nothing! Die!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000480, 'I choose the third option: KILLING YOU!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000481, 'As you wish...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000482, '<Harry takes the crystal from you and gently pats it.>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<Гарри бережно принимает кристалл из ваших рук и поглаживает его>'),
	(2000000483, 'Oh my precious! Did the big, mean whale hurt you? It\'ll be ok. I\'ll never let you out of my sight again!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ах, ты моя прелесть! Этот мерзкий кит тебя обидел? Ничего, теперь все будет хорошо. Больше я никому тебя не отдам!'),
	(2000000484, '<Harry looks up at you.>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<Гарри отрывается от созерцания шара и смотрит на вас.>'),
	(2000000485, 'So, where were we?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Так на чем мы остановились?'),
	(2000000486, 'From sundered ground the sacrament was stolen. The Shield of Aesirites is lost. Unrest will be eternal.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000487, 'The Staff of Storm\'s Fury pilfered. A curse upon this land! The storms will never cease!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000488, 'The Frozen Heart of Isuldof will consume this land until it is returned. Woe unto those that hold the heart as the curse of frozen blood besets them...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000489, 'The anguish of ten-thousand years awaits any foolish enough to don the Ancient Armor of the Kvaldir. Beware the mist and fog, mortals; for with them comes your end.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000491, 'Thank you for freeing me, $N! I\'m going to make my way to Shattrath!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
	(2000000492, 'It\'s good to finally see you, courier. Krasus has entrusted us with one of the few remaining copies of Ancient Dragonforged Blades.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Наконец-то ты прибыл. Крас доверил нам одну из немногих сохранившихся копий "Древних клинков драконьей ковки".'),
	(2000000493, '[Furbolg] Thank you, $N!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[Фурболг] Спасибо, $N!'),
	(2000000494, '[Furbolg] The prophecy is true!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[Фурболг] Предсказание сбылось!'),
	(2000000495, '[Furbolg] Those remaining at Stillpine Hold will welcome you as a hero!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[Фурболг] Живущие в Логове племени Тихвой будут встречать тебя как героя!'),
	(2000000496, '[Furbolg] The Stillpine furbolgs will not soon forget your bravery!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[Фурболг] Фурболги Тихвой не скоро забудут о вашей храбрости!'),
	(2000000497, 'What\'s this!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Что это?'),
	(2000000498, 'He... he kept it? All this time, he kept it!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Он... он хранил это... все это время?'),
	(2000000499, 'I knew!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Я знала!'),
	(2000000500, 'I sensed a part of him still alive! Trapped... struggling... Oh, Arthas!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Я чувствовала, что часть его души рвалась из оков... Боролась... О, Артас!'),
	(2000000501, 'Perhaps - perhaps he might someday remember what he once was.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Возможно... Однажды он вспомнит, каким он был когда-то.'),
	(2000000502, 'By the Light, may he at last find rest, free from the icy grip of that terrible blade.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Да упокоится он с миром, освободившись от ледяной хватки этого страшного клинка...'),
	(2000000519, 'Oh, lad...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ох, дружок...'),
	(2000000520, 'How I miss those endless days in Lordaeron...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Вернуть бы те славные лордеронские деньки...'),
	(2000000521, '...sharpenin\' yer skill with this dull blade...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '...когда мы бились на тупых мечах...'),
	(2000000522, '...forgin\' ya into a weapon meant to withstand the demands of a great destiny.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '...и готовили тебя к будущим великим свершениям...'),
	(2000000523, 'Heh... Yeh sure put them skills ta use, didn\'t yeh, lad?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Даа... Ты уж наверное не раз использовал те навыки, а?'),
	(2000000524, 'If only I\'da been able ta stop yeh that day, how different things mighta been.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Если бы я только остановил тебя тогда, все бы могло обернуться иначе.'),
	(2000000525, 'If only I\'da never discovered that accursed blade...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Если бы я только не нашел этот проклятый меч...'),
	(2000000526, 'Farewell, Arthas... my brother.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Прощай, Артас... брат мой.'),
	(2000000503, 'So, it is done.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Итак, все кончено.'),
	(2000000504, 'I had not dared to trust my senses - too many times has the Lich King made me to be a fool.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Я чувствовала, но не могла поверить - слишком часто Король-лич оставлял меня в дураках.'),
	(2000000505, 'Finally, he has been made to pay for the atrocities he imposed upon my people.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Наконец-то он поплатился за все страдания, на которые он обрек мой народ.'),
	(2000000506, 'May Azeroth never fail to remember the terrible price we paid for our weakness... for our pride.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Пускай же грядущие поколения всегда помнят, какова цена слабости... цена гордыни.'),
	(2000000507, 'But what now, hero? What of those freed from his grasp, but still shackled to their mortal coils?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Но что будет с теми, кто освободившись от его власти, остаются узниками своих бренных тел?'),
	(2000000508, 'Leave me.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Оставь меня.'),
	(2000000509, 'I have much to ponder.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Мне нужно о многом подумать.'),
	(2000000510, 'Arthas...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Артас...'),
	(2000000511, 'Alas, hero of Azeroth, you give me a greater gift than you know.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Славный герой!Ты сделал для меня больше, чем можешь представить.'),
	(2000000512, 'Long have I struggled to forgive the prince for his terrible transgressions.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Я долго пытался простить принца за его ужасные прегрешения.'),
	(2000000513, 'My soul has been wracked with unbearable anxiety, dark thoughts... distancing me from the Light.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Моя душа рвалась в невыносимых терзаниях... черные мысли застилали Свет.'),
	(2000000514, 'I recall clearly the gleam of pride in his eye as he stood before me, eager to defeat the enemies of the Light...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Я отчетливо помню гордый взгляд Артаса, исполненного решимости дать отпор врагам Света...'),
	(2000000515, 'Eager to defend his people, no matter the cost.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'готового защищать свой народ любой ценой...'),
	(2000000516, 'It is this memory of Arthas that I choose to keep in my heart.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Именно этот образ останется в моем сердце.'),
	(2000000517, 'I shall always be in your debt, friend.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Я в неоплатном долгу перед тобой, друг.'),
	(2000000518, 'Thank you.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Благодарю.'),
	(2000000527, 'Darion, my son.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Дарион, сын мой.'),
	(2000000528, 'At last, I am able to lay my eyes upon you again.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Наконец-то я могу положить свой взор на вас снова.'),
	(2000000529, 'The Lich King tormented me without end, Darion.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Король-лич подвергал меня бесконечным терзаниям, Дарион.'),
	(2000000530, 'Endlessly, he sought to break my will, to force me to serve him, to bind me to his blade...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Он все время пытался сломить мою волю и заставить служить ему, подчинить своему мечу...'),
	(2000000531, 'Finally, when events demanded his full attention, he left me.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Но когда события потребовали его вмешательства, он оставил меня.'),
	(2000000532, 'The one memory, I clung to, Darion... The one thought that kept me from giving in...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Меня всегда поддерживало одно воспоминание Дарион... Одна мысль, которая не позволяла сдаться...'),
	(2000000533, 'It was your sacrifice, my son, that again saved me from eternal peril.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Так твоя жертва, сын мой, вновь спасла меня от вечной агонии.'),
	(2000000534, 'Father...', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Отец...'),
	(2000000535, 'Father. I feared for your... your sanity.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Отец. Я боялся за твое... твое здравомыслие.'),
